query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 0 AND q1.view_count <= 100
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 1 AND u1.upvotes <= 100
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('bootstrap',
'delphi',
'excel',
'mysqli',
'object-oriented',
'oracle',
'pandas',
'ruby',
'spring',
'unity3d',
'vue.js',
'алгоритм',
'база-данных',
'вёрстка',
'строки')
inner join answer AS a1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('apple',
'codereview',
'english',
'pt',
'ru') group by t1.name;
